{
  "meta": {
    "schemaVersion": "1.0.0",
    "name": "day-end",
    "description": "End of day — advance day counter (deterministic), update game stage, check phone unlocks",
    "inputs": [],
    "outputs": [
      {
        "name": "result",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "read-day",
        "type": "ReadState",
        "label": "Read current day",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "key", "type": "string", "defaultValue": "day" }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "value", "type": "any" },
          { "name": "exists", "type": "boolean" }
        ],
        "config": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "increment-day",
        "type": "ComputeState",
        "label": "day + 1",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "value", "type": "any" }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "result", "type": "any" },
          { "name": "success", "type": "boolean" }
        ],
        "config": {
          "operation": "increment",
          "operand": 1
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "write-day",
        "type": "ModifyState",
        "label": "Write new day",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "key", "type": "string", "defaultValue": "day" },
          { "name": "value", "type": "any" }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "success", "type": "boolean" }
        ],
        "config": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "prompt-build",
        "type": "PromptBuild",
        "label": "Stage check prompt",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "object",
            "defaultValue": {}
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "messages", "type": "ChatMessage[]" },
          { "name": "text", "type": "string" },
          { "name": "estimatedTokens", "type": "number" }
        ],
        "config": {
          "defaultRole": "system",
          "fragments": [
            {
              "type": "base",
              "id": "role",
              "content": "你是一个纯逻辑计算器。day已经由引擎自动递增完毕，你只需要根据nextDay的值判断游戏阶段和手机解锁状态。\n\n注意：day字段已经是递增后的新值（nextDay），不需要你再+1。\n\n判断规则：\n1. 游戏阶段：day 1-9=adaptation, 10-18=investigation, 19-27=deepening, 28-36=endgame\n2. 手机解锁：day>=2则social=true, day>=4则dm=true, day>=7则forum=true, day>=14则anon=true\n3. 如果day>36，设gameOver=true并计算结局轴\n\n结局轴（仅day>36时）：\n- 真相深度轴：所有线≤1=surface, 任一线≥3=middle, 两线≥3且convergenceDiscovered=deep\n- 人际影响轴：拯救≥4=guardian, 拯救2-3+深渊1-2=catalyst, 旁观≥4=bystander, 深渊≥3=destroyer\n\n输出严格JSON（不要包裹在代码块中）：\n{\"stateChanges\":{\"gameStage\":\"阶段名\",\"phoneUnlocked_social\":bool,\"phoneUnlocked_dm\":bool,\"phoneUnlocked_forum\":bool,\"phoneUnlocked_anon\":bool}}\n\n示例：day=3 → {\"stateChanges\":{\"gameStage\":\"adaptation\",\"phoneUnlocked_social\":true,\"phoneUnlocked_dm\":false,\"phoneUnlocked_forum\":false,\"phoneUnlocked_anon\":false}}\n示例：day=7 → {\"stateChanges\":{\"gameStage\":\"adaptation\",\"phoneUnlocked_social\":true,\"phoneUnlocked_dm\":true,\"phoneUnlocked_forum\":true,\"phoneUnlocked_anon\":false}}\n示例：day=14 → {\"stateChanges\":{\"gameStage\":\"investigation\",\"phoneUnlocked_social\":true,\"phoneUnlocked_dm\":true,\"phoneUnlocked_forum\":true,\"phoneUnlocked_anon\":true}}",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "day",
              "source": "state.day",
              "label": "day（已递增后的新天数，直接用此值判断）"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineA",
              "source": "state.lineA_depth",
              "label": "Line A深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineB",
              "source": "state.lineB_depth",
              "label": "Line B深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "lineC",
              "source": "state.lineC_depth",
              "label": "Line C深度"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "convergence",
              "source": "state.convergenceDiscovered",
              "label": "汇聚已发现"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "npcFates",
              "source": "state.npcFates",
              "label": "NPC命运"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "generate",
        "type": "GenerateText",
        "label": "Calculate stage",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "messages", "type": "ChatMessage[]" }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "text", "type": "string" },
          { "name": "usage", "type": "object" }
        ],
        "config": {
          "responseFormat": "json",
          "temperature": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "json-parse",
        "type": "JSONParse",
        "label": "Parse",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "text", "type": "string", "required": true }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "data", "type": "object" },
          { "name": "success", "type": "boolean" },
          { "name": "error", "type": "string" }
        ],
        "config": {
          "extractFromCodeBlock": true,
          "fixCommonErrors": true,
          "fixTruncated": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "apply-state",
        "type": "ApplyState",
        "label": "Apply stage",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "changes", "type": "object", "required": true }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "applied", "type": "array" },
          { "name": "success", "type": "boolean" }
        ],
        "config": {
          "path": "stateChanges",
          "allowedKeys": [
            "gameStage",
            "gameOver",
            "phoneUnlocked_social",
            "phoneUnlocked_dm",
            "phoneUnlocked_forum",
            "phoneUnlocked_anon",
            "endingTruthAxis",
            "endingImpactAxis"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "signal-out",
        "type": "SignalOut",
        "label": "Output",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "data", "type": "string" }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "data", "type": "string" }
        ],
        "config": {
          "channel": "result"
        }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "source": "read-day",
        "sourceHandle": "value",
        "target": "increment-day",
        "targetHandle": "value"
      },
      {
        "source": "increment-day",
        "sourceHandle": "result",
        "target": "write-day",
        "targetHandle": "value"
      },
      {
        "source": "prompt-build",
        "sourceHandle": "messages",
        "target": "generate",
        "targetHandle": "messages"
      },
      {
        "source": "generate",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "json-parse",
        "targetHandle": "text"
      },
      {
        "source": "generate",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "signal-out",
        "targetHandle": "data"
      },
      {
        "source": "json-parse",
        "sourceHandle": "data",
        "target": "apply-state",
        "targetHandle": "changes"
      }
    ]
  }
}